headline: Dow Jones Leader Plows To New Highs As Gold Stock Glows
summary: Caterpillar plowed its way to an all-time high just ahead of earnings this week. Kinross Gold also scored a high after earnings.

headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock for Long-Term Investors and 2 We Turn Down
summary: A company that generates cash isn’t automatically a winner. Some businesses stockpile cash but fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their ability to expand.
